%%{init: {"theme": "base"}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant A as Agente IA
    participant PY as portals.yml
    participant WS as WebSearch (LLM)
    participant W as Playwright
    participant PL as pipeline.md
    participant H as scan-history.tsv

    Note over A: Após Níveis 0–2; local_parser_ok já populado

    A->>PY: Lê search_queries enabled

    loop cada query
        A->>WS: Executa query site:...
        WS-->>A: Snippets título + URL
        A->>A: Parse title/company (regex)
        A->>A: Descarta se company ∈ local_parser_ok
        A->>A: Acumula candidatos L3
    end

    A->>A: Merge + dedup com N0–N2
    A->>A: title_filter + location_filter

    loop cada URL nova só do Nível 3
        A->>W: browser_navigate (sequencial)
        W-->>A: snapshot conteúdo
        alt expirada / erro nav
            A->>H: skipped_expired
        else ativa (JD + Apply)
            A->>PL: - [ ] url | company | title
            A->>H: status added
        end
    end

    A-->>A: Resumo: expiradas descartadas, novas no pipeline
